__package__.yml.rawContents:
types:
  CreateRequestCustomAttributeDefinition:
    properties:
      key: optional<string>
      name: optional<string>
      schema: optional<map<string, unknown>>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
    inline: true
  CreateResponse:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    create:
      path: /v2/customers/custom-attribute-definitions
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        name: CreateRequest
        body:
          properties:
            custom_attribute_definition: optional<CreateRequestCustomAttributeDefinition>
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: CreateResponse
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            custom_attribute_definition:
              key: favoriteShow
              name: Favorite Show
              schema:
                $ref: >-
                  https://developer-production-s3.s3.amazonaws.com/schema.json#type
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Test $ref in examples bug
headers:
  Square-Version:
    type: optional<string>
